'''巴德西島'''（{{lang-en|Bardsey Island}}，{{lang-cy|Ynys Enlli}}）是位於[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]的一個[[島嶼|島嶼]]，在行政區劃上屬於格溫內斯<ref>[http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/53155/Bardsey-Island Encyclopaedia Britannica : ''Bardsey Island''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/53155/Bardsey-Island |date=20150503121524 }} Retrieved 16 August 2009</ref>。巴德西島面積{{convert|0.6|mi|km|1}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Ynys Enlli|url=http://www.ccgc.gov.uk/landscape--wildlife/protecting-our-landscape/special-landscapes--sites/protected-landscape/national-nature-reserves/ynys-enlli.aspx|publisher=Natural Resources Wales|accessdate=27 May 2014|archivedate=2014-12-09|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20141209164638/http://www.ccgc.gov.uk/landscape--wildlife/protecting-our-landscape/special-landscapes--sites/protected-landscape/national-nature-reserves/ynys-enlli.aspx}}</ref>，是一個重要的信仰中心，並且以其的自然而著稱。
